ender bathroom because my child does not know what they are is just plain stupid.  why do we allow such stupidity.   what everyone fears the most is the word GOD because they don't know.  Open up a bible and you will find your answers. what they teach in public school is ridiculous and i personally do not want my child to be subjected to ignorance.  i am sorry but i did not come from apes nor a dish or a big poof in the air and I just appeared one day.  if a parent wants to send their kids to private school what give you the right to criticize them.  blame the government for the issue that the public schools have.  kids are vulnerable at any age, why would i want my kids to know any different than what i have learned and was thought by my grandmother who was a teacher. "/><type4:DocumentMetaData xmi:id="13" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1087" language="en" documentId="2694" isLastSegment="false"/><types:WebArgumentMetadata xmi:id="24" sofa="1" begin="0" end="0" author="Kahu186" date="Aug 29, 2013 8:27PM" docType="artcomment" origUrl="http://living.msn.com/family-parenting/the-family-room-blog-post?post=ab228ffc-1e99-4b37-a7b8-0b6a4c3fb240" topic="public-private-schools" thumbsUp="10" thumbsDown="0" origId="2694" notes="" title="Is it wrong to send kids to private school?"/><type6:Paragraph xmi:id="39" sofa="1" begin="0" end="1087"/><cas:View sofa="1" members="13 24 39"/></xmi:XMI>